{"tid":879073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"售票員怕說外文　新宿御苑700萬門票「免費送」","createTime":"2018-10-27T15:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T05:33:03.000Z","uid":32511,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"dba65a93973e6e874d052918348b4a1b44a4b0f0","tid":879073,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:46:08.000Z","msg":"日本東京新宿御苑是著名的賞櫻、賞楓觀光景點，但現在卻爆出有一名職員因為怕說外文，看到外國觀光客來訪，就大方將門票「免費送」，2年半下來，初估導致新宿御苑損失了2500萬日圓(約新台幣700萬元)。<br />\n <br />\n據日本《NHK》報導，這名73歲的男職員長期負責售票窗口，但他因為害怕講外文，自認為「菜英文」，一但看到外國遊客，就自動「免費送票」，並擅自刪除發放門票的相關數據。該案件在去年年初被發現，經調查發現該名男職員「免費送票」的行為已長達2年半，估計造成新宿御苑約少收2500萬日圓的門票費。新宿御苑的收費標準為成人200日圓，半票為50日圓。<br />\n <br />\n據悉事件爆發時，該名職員被罰減去1個月薪水，隨後這名職員也辭職。"},{"pid":"cecb713c0cdabf8d0c87945f85bf2129070126d0","tid":879073,"uid":157138,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:47:45.000Z","msg":"73歲仲成個小學生咁去逃避問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414f5f1adbaa363eac5755ea978b263f34b825a4","tid":879073,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0267ddddfa5778ca893e87c91a600a513c4b8c43","tid":879073,"uid":80072,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:49:35.000Z","msg":"收錢要用好多英文？"},{"pid":"48252e568d112532a81c8f152be6874badb82f8f","tid":879073,"uid":216553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:52:05.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fdc5f6099395a339c48265829d66022a1615685","tid":879073,"uid":550,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0267ddddfa5778ca893e87c91a600a513c4b8c43","tid":879073,"uid":80072,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:49:35.000Z","msg":"收錢要用好多英文？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:52:53.000Z",